Sonia Mugabo ni Umunyarwanda kazi wihangiye imirimo akaba umunyamideri ndetse akaba numwe mu bagore babikora nk'umwuga mu Rwanda. Niwe washinze ikigo '''''Sonia Mugabo''''' akaba akibereye n'umuyobozi mukuru ndetse n'umuhanzi w'imideri''.''

== Amateka ==
Sonia Mugabo yavutse tariki 5 zukwa gatanu 1990 avukira I kigali. Muri genocide yo 1994 yabaye afite imyaka ine, aho yaje guhura nihungabana ryinshi nyuma yo kurokokera kwa gisimba n'umuryango we mugari muri jenocide yakorewe abatutsi<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/opinions/today-i-will-share-my-testimony-sonia-mugabo</ref>. Akaba yarize amashuri yisumbuye muri greenhills academy, aza gukomereza amashuri ye muri buena vista university<ref>https://www.bvu.edu/</ref> mu gihugu cya leta zunze ubumwe za america, akaba yarize ibigendanye n'itumanaho n'imideri (communication and design).
